      <title>中国与阿联酋就增加两国间航班进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/china-uae-said-in-talks-to-increase-flights-between-two-nations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来，旅游业增长一直停滞不前，中国和阿联酋正寻求增加双边航权，此举旨在促进两国之间的贸易和旅游业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/china-uae-said-in-talks-to-increase-flights-between-two-nations</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 13:41:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿美下调 8 月份亚洲原油价格 因需求减弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/aramco-cuts-aug-crude-prices-to-asia-in-sign-of-weaker-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿美公司连续第二个月下调销往亚洲的所有等级原油价格，这一迹象表明，全球最大的原油出口国认为其主要市场的需求持续疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/aramco-cuts-aug-crude-prices-to-asia-in-sign-of-weaker-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 13:39:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国主导的七国集团债务增加引发标普和范围担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/us-led-debt-increase-across-g-7-stokes-s-p-and-scope-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两家信用评估公司强调了美国和发达国家债务持续上升的问题，标准普尔全球评级警告称，只有巨大的市场压力才能改变这一轨迹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/us-led-debt-increase-across-g-7-stokes-s-p-and-scope-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 12:43:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲 IPO 将难以维持上半年的反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/european-ipos-will-struggle-to-sustain-their-first-half-rebound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于政治不确定性和股市动荡，寻求上市的发行人数量减少，欧洲首次公开募股 (IPO) 上半年的强劲表现不太可能在今年剩余时间内持续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/european-ipos-will-struggle-to-sustain-their-first-half-rebound</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 12:42:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易商评估干旱越南降雨情况 罗布斯塔咖啡价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/robusta-coffee-gains-as-traders-assess-rains-in-parched-vietnam</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心咖啡产量可能下降，交易商密切关注全球最大咖啡生产国越南的降雨量，导致罗布斯塔咖啡期货上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/robusta-coffee-gains-as-traders-assess-rains-in-parched-vietnam</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 12:38:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>监管机构称，到 2027 年，澳大利亚将面临天然气短缺的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/australia-runs-the-risk-of-gas-shortfall-by-2027-watchdog-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项独立调查显示，作为全球最大的液化天然气运输国之一的澳大利亚将在两年多一点的时间内面临液化天然气短缺，该调查敦促该国提高产量以应对不断增长的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/australia-runs-the-risk-of-gas-shortfall-by-2027-watchdog-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲需求疲软导致油价从两个月高位回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于沙特阿拉伯连续第二个月下调对亚洲的石油价格，油价从两个月高点回落，表明该地区的需求持续疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 23:29:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市因选举而上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/asian-shares-head-for-gains-after-new-s-p-500-peak-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于关键选举成为焦点，且美国经济数据支持宽松政策，投资者对美联储降息变得更加乐观，欧洲股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/asian-shares-head-for-gains-after-new-s-p-500-peak-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 22:23:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿美和阿布扎比国家石油公司正在考虑竞购天然气生产商 Santos</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/aramco-adnoc-are-said-to-consider-bids-for-gas-producer-santos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，沙特阿美公司和阿布扎比国家石油公司一直在分别研究对桑托斯有限公司的潜在收购要约，这两家公司成为最新两家对这家澳大利亚生产商的液化天然气资产表现出兴趣的公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/aramco-adnoc-are-said-to-consider-bids-for-gas-producer-santos</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 20:13:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡与债券持有人达成重组协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/sri-lanka-bondholders-agree-on-core-terms-of-debt-restructuring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡与债权人达成了一项重组 126 亿美元债券的协议，使这个南亚国家在债务违约两年后更接近完成债务改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/sri-lanka-bondholders-agree-on-core-terms-of-debt-restructuring</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 15:49:28 GMT</pubDate>
